<sect1 id="dir_0cd17818026a7be52077794beeee002c_1autotoc_md190">
<title>Introduction</title><para><emphasis><bold><ref refid="namespace_luthetus_1_1_text_editor" kindref="compound">Luthetus.TextEditor</ref></bold></emphasis> is a Text Editor component library using the <ulink url="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/apps/aspnet/web-apps/blazor">Blazor UI Framework</ulink> for <ulink url="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/">.NET</ulink></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_0cd17818026a7be52077794beeee002c_1autotoc_md191">
<title>Goal</title><para>The aim of <ref refid="namespace_luthetus_1_1_text_editor" kindref="compound">Luthetus.TextEditor</ref> is to replicate the features of the <ulink url="https://microsoft.github.io/monaco-editor/">Monaco Editor</ulink> that powers <ulink url="https://code.visualstudio.com/">Visual Studio Code</ulink> using Blazor.</para>
<para>One can make use of this Text Editor by referencing the Nuget Package or cloning the source code and referencing it directly.</para>
</sect1>
